01:31:36.123 --> 01:31:38.887
No, please, no!

774
01:31:38.926 --> 01:31:41.690
Just seeing you here is--

775
01:31:41.728 --> 01:31:44.026
Come on,
get a move on!

776
01:31:46.442 --> 01:31:48.637
Please, stay by my side.

777
01:31:50.338 --> 01:31:52.772
Everybody off the bus.

778
01:31:52.807 --> 01:31:55.367
This is the last stop,
get off.

779
01:31:56.586 --> 01:31:58.816
Out!

780
01:33:35.610 --> 01:33:39.706
You idiot, we've been
waiting for four hours!

781
01:33:39.756 --> 01:33:42.156
We were sick with worry!

782
01:33:42.183 --> 01:33:44.651
- Shame on you!
- Shut your mouth!

783
01:33:44.693 --> 01:33:47.287
From now on,
you don't say a thing.

784
01:33:47.321 --> 01:33:49.983
Leave her alone.
Go away!

785
01:33:53.194 --> 01:33:56.186
Look what France
has done to me.

786
01:33:56.230 --> 01:33:59.222
My son's screaming at me
before the A'I'd.

787
01:34:22.790 --> 01:34:25.816
Tomorrow...

788
01:34:25.860 --> 01:34:29.352
I'll be the one
taking you to school.

